(last updated 2012-09-12)

Resource Identifier (RI) Scheme name: hcp
Status: provisional

Scheme syntax:
   hcp://system/<File>.htm (Where <File> is the file to load)

Scheme semantics:
   Displaying an help page on Microsoft Windows Help and Support Center.

Encoding considerations:
   Unknown, use with care.

Applications/protocols that use this scheme name:
   Works only on Windows XP. Later replaced by ms-help.

Interoperability considerations:
   Unknown, use with care.
Security considerations:
   Unknown, use with care.
Contact:
   Registering party: Alexey Melnikov <alexey.melnikov&isode.com>
   Scheme creator: Microsoft
Author/Change controller:
   Either the registering party or someone who is verified to represent
   the scheme creator.  See previous answer.
References:
   http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Microsoft_Windows_Help_and_Support_Center
